_sText:
Ported from CS:GO special for centralka.ru

Original map: 79330

Location: Set inside and outside a vast mountain cavern, this map offers a unique mix of advantages and disadvantages for both Prisoners and Guards. Tread carefully, as danger lurks in every corner.



Features:



       
  • 56 T Spawns - Multiple spawn points for Prisoners.

    •    
  • 24 CT Spawns - Strategic spawn areas for the Guards.

    •    
  • Cell Area - The main prison section where prisoners are held.

    •    
  • Gun Room - Arm yourself with weapons to stand a chance.

    •    
  • 2 Medics - Medical stations for healing.

    •    
  • Pool - Relax or take a risky dive.

    •    
  • Disco (Hidden) - A secret area for some unexpected fun.



Map Games Include:



       
  • Colours - A colorful game of survival.

    •    
  • Skipping - Fully automated skipping game.

    •    
  • Climb - Scale heights, including a Hard Mode via Lava Button.

    •    
  • Race - Race against time and your opponents.

    •    
  • Maze - Can you escape the labyrinth?

    •    
  • Tower Jump - A test of your jumping skills.

    •    
  • Minefield - Watch your step, it's dangerous!

    •    
  • Bunny Hop - Test your agility and reflexes.

    •    
  • Soccer - A working soccer ball for some friendly competition.

    •    
  • Four Corners - Choose your corner and survive the challenge.



Plenty of Secrets


Explore the map thoroughly to uncover hidden paths, secret rooms, and unexpected surprises!
